{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821110/extras/pageLogo.png?t=1736490534\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Synopsis</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Renata has been haunted her entire life by a void within. She needs to find answers that fill the gaps of her past. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> She follows a promising track to an abandoned military research base. However, she soon finds out that this place holds secrets beyond her comprehension and that her obsession might cost her a price she can't pay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821110/extras/gif04.gif?t=1736490534\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About the game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Subversive Memories is\u00a0set in a fictitious Brazil during the military dictatorship that took place from 1964 to 1985. It talks about the horrors of being oppressed by those who should protect us and the memories of the victims of a ruthless authoritarian regime that kidnapped, censored and killed thousands of people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game itself is heavily inspired by classic survival-horror games from the late 90s, employing retro 3d graphics, limited resources and an involving mystery that respects the players ability to put the all the pieces together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821110/extras/gif05.gif?t=1736490534\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore maze-like areas trying to find the answers you seek.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Protect yourself and engage combat only when necessary.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage your resources to survive each area and unfold the secrets.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find items to solve puzzles and progress.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Target of 2-3 hours of gameplay with replayability in mind.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Full controller support.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821110/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736490534","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821110/page.bg.jpg?t=1736490534","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821110/6f36ee9b03de73f59e1148bf18e738276c8fad93/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736490534","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821110/6f36ee9b03de73f59e1148bf18e738276c8fad93/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736490534","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"This Game may contain content not appropriate for all ages, or may not be appropriate for viewing at work: Frequent Violence or Gore, General Mature Content."},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3343620,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821110/extras/pageLogo.png?t=1736490534\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Synopsis</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Renata has been haunted her entire life by a void within. She needs to find answers that fill the gaps of her past. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> She follows a promising track to an abandoned military research base. However, she soon finds out that this place holds secrets beyond her comprehension and that her obsession might cost her a price she can't pay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img clas